{"tid":130735,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"濕9政府又一新搞作---綜援人士出雙糧","createTime":"2017-02-22T14:57:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T03:08:09.000Z","uid":67750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df33f662cb696068f55ea03520b2f087e2f8b483","tid":130735,"uid":67750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"派糖措施<br />\n援助基層措施：<br />\n<strong>1) 綜援派雙糧</strong>。<br />\n2) 針對65歲以上長者發行銀色債券 (Silver Bond)，首批為期三年。<br />\n3) 將逆按揭範圍擴展至未補價資助房屋<br />\n4) 每年撥款29億實施「低收入在職家庭津貼」。<br />\n中小企支援措施：<br />\n1) 寬減75%利得稅，上限2萬。<br />\n2) 寬免商業登記費。<br />\n3) 推出科技券，資助中小企使用科技服務及方案，每間中小企最多獲20萬元資助。<br />\n4) 延長「中小企融資擔保計劃」下「特別優惠措施」的申請期至2017年2月28日；降低擔保費年率一成；取消最低擔保費。<br />\n5) 成立20億元「創科創投基金」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打工仔份雙糧要攞晒去交稅<br />\n大陸新移民乜撚都唔做有綜援用 有公屋住<br />\n年尾有雙糧又唔駛交稅<br />\n唔駛返工 留喺屋企扑野 生多件又攞多d綜援<br />\n生多個又同香港人爭床位<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4933dc15929101fd73533fd5af9e700d35ef871","tid":130735,"uid":67750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T17:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71271c8b5f1e74240571f6e05fc87dbaf6bdc6fc","tid